Details


ITEM#: 10337907


Find a new level of comfort and protection as you whip down the snow covered slops with this Scott USA Ransom Goggle.

Kelly green frame
Amplifier chrome tinted lens
Hydrophilic anti-fog coating
Adjustable head strap
100-percent UVA/UVB protection
Hypoallergenic face foam
Dual lens
Helmet compatible






