Of course we had cut the tags at home. We put the helmet back on her head and tucked her jacket hood between the helmet and the back of her head so that she could ski comfortably.. Now that we are back home, I'm looking into putting duct tape or finding some extra bicycle helmet padding to attach or glue onto the helmet.

